oads/2023/11/Porno-For-Pyros-performing-800x572.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Porno-For-Pyros-performing-696x497.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Porno-For-Pyros-performing-1392x995.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Porno-For-Pyros-performing-1068x763.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/porno-for-pyros">Porno For Pyros</a>宣布在中断 26 年巡演后进行告别巡演，并分享他们即将推出的 EP 中的歌曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/porno-for-pyros-announce-release-of-first-song-in-26-years-agua-3534067">Agua</a> 》。</p><p>该乐队由 Perry Farrell、Stephen Perkins 和 Peter DiStefano 组成，将于 2024 年 2 月开始在 16 个城市进行巡演。他们将于 2 月 13 日在加利福尼亚州圣安娜天文台开始巡演，并穿越美国。</p><p>此后，Porno For Pyros 将在洛杉矶、丹佛、芝加哥、多伦多、波士顿、纽约等地停留，然后于 3 月 10 日在新泽西州蒙特克莱尔的威尔蒙特剧院结束演出。</p><p>门票将于当地时间 11 月 17 日星期五上午 10 点开始公开发售。 <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fporno-for-pyros-tickets%2Fartist%2F763399" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>购买门票。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Czq8LexLHBJ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"